column5: The weather was awesome, the bite not so much. Still managed a decent little Laker though and had lots of bumps. I've never seen so much bumping without hookups. I hope that's not an indication of what I can expect when I start my holidays next week. Hopefully the Big Rideau will open up and be nice to me. lol
That's one more lake trout than I've caught in my last 30+ kms of trolling.  Good job, hope the bites opens up for you in the coming week.
